---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="About" description="Justin Helmer — Principal Engineer.">
  <h1 class="page-heading">About</h1>
  <div class="about-text">
    <p>I started as a front-end designer, then moved into front-end technologies and frameworks, then into server-side technologies and systems. During the mobile boom, I spent time in large-scale e-commerce enterprise. I then spent the next five years helping build AI-powered optimization systems before the current wave.</p>
    <p>From there, I moved into large-scale platform engineering, solving increasingly hard problems at scale, most recently through M&A.</p>
    <p>Today I am building the future where anyone can harness the full capability of AI to realize their potential. The future is for the builders.</p>
    <p class="resume-line">
      <a href="/resume" class="resume-link" data-nav-item target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
        <span class="resume-text">the rest is on paper</span>
        <svg class="resume-arrow" width="13" height="13" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M7 17 17 7"/><path d="M7 7h10v10"/></svg>
      </a>
    </p>
  </div>
</Base>

<style>
  .about-text {
    max-width: 560px;
    font-size: 16px;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .about-text p + p {
    margin-top: 1.5em;
  }

  /* Understated résumé link — mono, muted, brightens on hover. */
  .resume-line {
    margin-top: 2.5em;
  }

  .resume-link {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 6px;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--text-tertiary);
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: color 0.15s, gap 0.15s;
  }

  .resume-text {
    border-bottom: 1px solid color-mix(in srgb, currentColor 25%, transparent);
    padding-bottom: 1px;
  }

  .resume-arrow {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    transition: transform 0.15s;
  }

  .resume-link:hover {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    gap: 8px;
  }

  .resume-link:hover .resume-arrow {
    transform: translate(1px, -1px);
  }
</style>
